        "scraping_time": "2024-05-20T07.00.05",
        "en_title": "IRAN, ELICOTTERO PRESIDENT RAISI Red and medium: all dead",
        "en_content": "\"Duro\" landing for Raisi helicopter The helicopter on which the Iranian President Raisi traveled and his entourage had an accident. According to the agency Meher the vehicle was forced to a rough landing in the Varzghan area for bad weather. Research is hampered by prohibitive weather conditions. Several rescue teams activated. The convoy was composed of 3 helicopters on which other authorities traveled. The incident occurred in the Persian Azerbaijan, where Raisi inaugurated a dam. The Khamenei Supreme Guide convened an emergency meeting of the Security Council.",
